//Instruction Page HOW TO... EDIT PROFILE ADD RENTAL PROPERTY DELETE RENTAL PROPERTY VIEW RENTAL PROPERTY CONTACT PROPERTY OWNERS
//Edit Profile Instructions HOW TO EDIT YOUR PROFILE 1.\tAfter Logging in, click the “My Profile” button on the bottom navigation 2.\tWhen on the “My Profile” page, tap on the top right icon 3.\tThis takes you to the “Profile Page”, where you can view all your details 4.\tTo edit your profile, click the “Edit” button on the right, which will navigate you to the “Edit Profile” page. 5.\tYou can then make changes to your profile details and click on the “SAVE” button
//Add Property Instruction HOW TO ADD YOUR PROPERTY 1.\tTo add your property to the app, click on the “Add Property” button on the bottom navigation 2.\tWhen on the “Add Property” page, click on the top right icon 3.\tYou will then be navigated to the “Add Rental Property” page 4.\tFill in all the details of your property and click “Upload Property” 5.\tThe property will then appear on the “My Properties” or ” Add Properties” page 6.\tWhen your property is uploaded, users will be able to view it and contact you if they are interested
//Delete Property Instruction HOW TO DELETE MY PROPERTY 1.\tTo delete your rental property, click on the “Add Property” button on the bottom navigation 2.\tHere you will have a list of all the properties you have uploaded 3.\tClick on the delete icon on the property you want to delete and then click yes on the confirmation dialog 4.\tThe property will then be deleted from the entire application
//View Rental Property Instruction HOW TO VIEW RENTAL PROPERTIES 1.\tTo view a property, simply tap on the desired property on the dashboard page 2.\tYou will be redirected to the “Property Details” page, where you can take a look at more information about that particular property including the property owner’s details.
//Contact Rental Property Owner Instruction HOW TO CONTACT PROPERTY OWNERS 1.\tTo contact a property owner, simply tap on the desired property on the dashboard page. 2.\tYou will be redirected to the “Property Details” page, where you can simply scroll down and view the property owner’s contact details, which include WhatsApp, Email, SMS or you can simply give them a call.
